          <br>
          <p class="advantages-text">We offer systems that resemble bottled-water coolers, but instead of a heavy 5-gallon bottle on top we install our CWSA-Double Filtration system on the back of the self-standing and countertop models. These systems bring delicious, refreshing filtered water right into your home or office. Both the countertop and self-standing models provide hot and cold water. </p>
          <p class="advantages-text"><strong>Next-day service throughout the NY Metro area</strong></p>
          
